547
01:00:46.560 --> 01:00:48.449
My face hurts.

548
01:00:50.400 --> 01:00:51.640
Why?

549
01:00:52.880 --> 01:00:57.124
Why...
Why does my face hurt?

550
01:00:58.720 --> 01:00:59.767
Baby.

551
01:01:01.520 --> 01:01:02.521
Nat.

552
