so bad right now.

556
01:01:55.800 --> 01:01:59.646
I just don't want to
become the devil's bitch.

557
01:02:03.760 --> 01:02:05.524
I'm going to do
what I got to do.

558
01:02:07.680 --> 01:02:10.206
I'm going to do
what I got to do. Okay?

559
01:02:58.240 --> 01:02:59.810
I'm sorry. Mia.

560
01:03:01.320 --> 01:03:02.446
