569
01:03:37.040 --> 01:03:38.326
I can't do this.

570
01:03:41.160 --> 01:03:42.730
I can't do this.

571
01:04:16.840 --> 01:04:21.129
This time the only fucking
way is the hard way!

572
01:05:01.760 --> 01:05:03.569
David.

573
01:05:04.760 --> 01:05:07.081
Murderer.

574
01:05:08.800 --> 01:05:10.370
Coward.

575
01:07:12.680 --> 01:07:14.170
Eric.

576
01:07:34.440 --> 01:07:35.441
Hey. Okay?

577
01:07:38.480 --> 01:07:39.527
David.

578
01:07:41.480 --> 01:07:43.130
I missed you. man.

579
01:07:47.440 --> 01:07:49.727
You know that. buddy.

580
01:09:09.920 --> 01:09:11.160
David?

581
01:09:13.600 --> 01:09:15.204
David?

582
01:09:15.720 --> 01:09:18.929
I can't move!
I can't breathe!

583
01:09:19.440 --> 01:09:20.930
David!

584
01:09:21.640 --> 01:09:23.404
Help me!

585
01:09:24.680 --> 01:09:26.364
Help me. David!

586
01:09:26.720 --> 01:09:28.051
You're not her.

587
01:09:28.200 --> 01:09:29.850
David!

588
01:09:30.280 --> 01:09:31.281
Help me!

589
01:09:32.160 --> 01:09:33.525
You're not her!

590
01:09:40.360 --> 01:09:42.362
