coming to see her.

599
01:10:07.880 --> 01:10:10.247
Like you promised.

600
01:10:10.920 --> 01:10:12.684
But you never did.

601
01:10:14.080 --> 01:10:17.050
Please stop it.
I'm begging you.

602
01:10:18.520 --> 01:10:21.649
I know Mother
hates you now.

603
01:10:21.720 --> 01:10:23.529
and she waits for you
in hell.

604
01:10:33.040 --> 01:10:35.725
Shut up. Shut up.

605
01:10:53.160 --> 01:10:55.049
I'm so sorry.

606
01:10:59.160 --> 01:11:00.685
I should have been there.

607
01:11:02.680 --> 01:11:05.286
I should have
been there for you.

608
01:12:00.440 --> 01:12:02.169
Come on.
Please. come back.

609
01:12:09.000 --> 01:12:11.401
Come on. Mia.
Come back to me. please!

610
01:12:55.120 --> 01:12:57.407
Okay. you are at peace.

611
01:12:58.840 --> 01:13:00.729
You are at peace now.

612
01:13:27.400 --> 01:13:28.401
David?

613
01:13:35.080 --> 01:13:36.411
Mia?

614
01:13:43.240 --> 01:13:44.924
It was so horrible.

615
01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:49.042
It was so horrible.

616
01:13:49.760 --> 01:13:53.321
It's okay.
It's all over now.

617
01:13:56.760 --> 01:13:59.684
Thanks for not
leaving me. David.

618
01:14:08.280 --> 01:14:11.090
Wait here. I'm going
to get the car keys.

619
01:14:11.240 --> 01:14:13.049
Okay?
Yeah.

620
01:15:16.840 --> 01:15:17.841
David!

621
01:15:18.760 --> 01:15:20.649
Go. Please. go.

622
01:15:20.720 --> 01:15:21.721
Go!

623
01:15:22.040 --> 01:15:25.283
I'm not going to go anywhere.
I'm not going anywhere!

624
01:15:29.520 --> 01:15:31.602
Here. take the keys.
Look at me. let's go.

625
01:15:31.760 --> 01:15:33.364
Come on. Let's go.

626
01:15:39.160 --> 01:15:40.571
Get out of here.

627
01:15:41.960 --> 01:15:45.089
No! No!

628
01:15:45.240 --> 01:15:46.321
David!

629
01:15:47.200 --> 01:15:49.009
David!

630
01:15:52.520 --> 01:15:55.046
No! No!

631
01:15:55.440 --> 01:15:58.603
David! David!

632
01:16:07.640 --> 01:16:10.246
He's coming.

633
01:18:42.880 --> 01:18:45.042
Mia.

634
01:19:43.720 --> 01:19:45.324
Come here. you bitch!

635
01:21:10.680 --> 01:21:11.966
Come on.

636
01:22:09.880 --> 01:22:12.690
You're going to die here.
you pathetic junkie!

637
01:22:15.040 --> 01:22:17.725
I've had enough
of this shit.

638
01:22:54.520 --> 01:22:58.002
I will feast on your soul.

639
01:23:01.080 --> 01:23:03.287
Feast on this. motherfucker!

640
01:23:15.520 --> 01:23:17.363
Die!

641
01:23:38.280 --> 01:23:40.282
Go back to Hell. bitch.

642
01:29:29.120 --> 01:29:32.090
I believe I
have made a significant find

643
01:29:32.160 --> 01:29:34.049
in the Candarian Ruins...

644
01:29:34.200 --> 01:29:36.680
a volume of ancient
Sumerian burial practices

645
01:29:36.760 --> 01:29:38.808
and funerary incantations.

646
01:29:39.400 --> 01:29:42.483
It is entitled
"Naturom Demonto."

647
01:29:42.640 --> 01:29:45.211
Roughly translated.
"Book of the Dead."

648
01:29:45.400 --> 01:29:49.405
The book is bound in human flesh
and inked in human blood.

649
01:29:49.720 --> 01:29:53.008
It deals with demons.
demon resurrection...

650
01:29:53.200 --> 01:29:55.089
those forces
which roam the forest

651
01:29:55.240 --> 01:29:57.163
and dark bowers
of man's domain.

652
01:29:58.120 --> 01:30:01.169
The first few pages warn that
these enduring creatures...

653
01:30:01.320 --> 01:30:04.324
may lie dormant
but are never truly dead.

654
01:30:04.920 --> 01:30:06.763
They may be recalled
to active life

655
01:30:06.880 --> 01:30:09.360
through the incantations
presented in this book.

656
01:30:09.520 --> 01:30:12.091
It is through recitation
of these passages

657
01:30:12.160 --> 01:30:13.525
that the demons
are given license...

658
01:30:14.200 --> 01:30:16.168
to possess the living.

659
01:30:49.520 --> 01:30:52.285
I have seen the dark shadows
moving in the woods...

660
01:30:52.440 --> 01:30:55.046
and I have no doubt that
whatever I have resurrected

661
01:30:55.120 --> 01:30:56.326
through this book...

662
01:30:56.480 --> 01:30:59.768
is sure to come
calling for me.

663
01:31:10.720 --> 01:31:12.245
Groovy.
